{
  "stem": "8916.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went to-- to a barrack in Plaszow It was the fortunate thing that I did, right.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was not smart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just, I think I probably just wanted to go with my-- where my mother went.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just saw my mother leave, so I-- I just tried to get out and I made it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was-- the thing that was ironic is that I-- I left a ghetto which was hell, and I got to-- to this Plaszow, which was more-- worse than hell because that was the camp where Amon Goth was the commandant, the person who liked to shoot people from the balcony and also point blank and-- and did other atrocities during his tenure.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1943.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About-- in the fall of '43.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at first--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so at first the-- the-- first of all the camp was still in transition.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was still be built and construction was still going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So most of those people who were not assigned to specific jobs in specific factories were assigned to work at random to-- at different locations in construction.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I worked at places like building roads and helping construct barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was hoping no one would notice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I did the work of a-- of a grown man, hauling dirt, and breaking up grave markers, and building that road that was actually depicted in the movie called",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It seemed like-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It seemed like-- as if, you know, things were so unreal that to break up somebody's tombstone wasn't anything in comparison to what was being-- what was happening to live people.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were always hear about so many people got shot today.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
